#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.applymap.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.applymap"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.df_map:1 of
msgid "Apply a function to a Dataframe elementwise."
msgstr "对 DataFrame 的每个元素应用一个函数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.df_map:3 of
msgid ""
"This method applies a function that accepts and returns a scalar to every"
" element of a DataFrame."
msgstr "此方法将一个接受并返回标量的函数应用于 DataFrame 的每个元素。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.df_map of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.df_map:6 of
msgid "Python function, returns a single value from a single value."
msgstr "Python 函数，从单个值返回单个值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.df_map:8 of
msgid "If 'ignore', propagate NaN values, without passing them to func."
msgstr "如果为 'ignore'，则传播 NaN 值，而不将其传递给 func。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.df_map:10 of
msgid "Specify dtypes of returned DataFrames."
msgstr "指定返回的 DataFrame 的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.df_map:12 of
msgid ""
"Specify dtypes of all columns of returned DataFrames, only effective when"
" dtypes is not specified."
msgstr "指定返回的 DataFrame 所有列的数据类型，仅在未指定 dtypes 时有效。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.df_map:15 of
msgid "Whether infer dtypes when dtypes or dtype is not specified."
msgstr "当未指定 dtypes 或 dtype 时是否推断数据类型。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.df_map:17 of
msgid "Additional keyword arguments to pass as keywords arguments to `func`."
msgstr "传递给 `func` 的额外关键字参数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.df_map of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.df_map:20 of
msgid "Transformed DataFrame."
msgstr "转换后的 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.df_map of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.df_map:25 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.apply`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.df_map:26 of
msgid "Apply a function along input axis of DataFrame."
msgstr "沿 DataFrame 的输入轴应用函数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.df_map:28 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.replace`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.df_map:29 of
msgid "Replace values given in `to_replace` with `value`."
msgstr "将 `to_replace` 中的值替换为 `value`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.df_map:31 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.map`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.df_map:32 of
msgid "Apply a function elementwise on a Series."
msgstr "对 Series 的每个元素应用函数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.df_map:35 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.df_map:48 of
msgid "Like Series.map, NA values can be ignored:"
msgstr "与 Series.map 类似，可以忽略 NA 值："

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.df_map:57 of
msgid ""
"It is also possible to use `map` with functions that are not `lambda` "
"functions:"
msgstr "也可以使用非 `lambda` 函数与 `map` 一起使用："

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.df_map:65 of
msgid ""
"Note that a vectorized version of `func` often exists, which will be much"
" faster. You could square each number elementwise."
msgstr ""
"注意，通常存在 `func` 的向量化版本，其速度会快得多。你可以对每个数字进行"
"逐元素平方。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.df_map:73 of
msgid "But it's better to avoid map in that case."
msgstr "但在这种情况下最好避免使用 map。"

